Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:05.68,Title,,0000,0000,0000,,FAMOUS DETECTIVE HOLMES
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.06,0:01:41.02,Ep Title,,0000,0000,0000,,Buzz Buzz!\NThe Fly Fly Mecha Operation
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.88,0:02:09.48,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Oops!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.05,0:02:12.81,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Professor, I can't hold on any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.96,0:02:15.79,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Deal with it!\NWe're almost to the jewels.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.96,0:02:18.22,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,This is nothing, just a trifle.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.24,0:02:33.57,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... I hate that sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.62,0:02:43.24,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Phew... we finally made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.55,0:02:44.52,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Shh! Quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.79,0:02:51.42,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,P... Professor, somebody's there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.17,0:02:57.63,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, that diamond!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.04,0:03:01.02,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.21,0:03:11.58,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.85,0:03:13.34,Behind the Scenes,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that noise?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.39,0:03:14.28,Behind the Scenes,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.48,0:03:15.35,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, rats!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.49,0:03:19.18,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.49,0:03:22.79,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,No! No, we haven't\Nstolen anything... yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.33,0:03:25.85,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh well... Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.83,0:03:27.82,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.00,0:03:37.51,Behind the Scenes,,0000,0000,0000,,- Thief!\N- Get them!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.51,0:03:38.80,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,- This is bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.51,0:03:38.80,Behind the Scenes,,0000,0000,0000,,- After them!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.17,0:03:39.97,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry! Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.84,0:03:43.82,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Professor, how come things\Nalways end up this way?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.83,0:03:45.82,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,As if I should know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.69,0:03:59.49,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Inspector!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.41,0:04:02.04,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Holmes, why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.72,0:04:04.74,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm investigating the case at the\Nrequest of the store owner.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.55,0:04:09.85,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,From the eyewitness's testimony,\Nthere's no doubt!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.06,0:04:11.39,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,This was the work of\NMoriarty and his gang.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.39,0:04:12.52,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to investigate.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.89,0:04:14.48,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Those three again...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.59,0:04:16.72,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard there was something\Nleft at the scene of the crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.70,0:04:18.96,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Bring it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.96,0:04:19.62,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.40,0:04:23.70,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,This is what was left in the safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.21,0:04:27.54,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,How irritating!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.91,0:04:30.53,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,They left an announcement of\Ntheir next caper, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.41,0:04:32.27,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.08,0:04:35.05,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.25,0:04:36.87,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,"This was a mere trial run.\NBe forewarned:
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.08,0:04:40.25,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,The fine royal horse,\NShoscom Prince, is next."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.59,0:04:42.95,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,So, those three\Nescaped through this window?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.16,0:04:47.15,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,No, through the other window,\Naccording to the witnesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.89,0:04:50.56,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Fragments of broken glass are\Nscattered only on the outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.83,0:04:53.39,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,This means that the window\Nwas shattered from the inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.77,0:04:57.17,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you're saying that they\Nintentionally broke this window first...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.54,0:04:59.47,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,then escaped through the other one?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.64,0:05:00.47,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.07,0:05:04.07,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,This was simply a failed\Nattempt at cheap camouflage.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.51,0:05:08.00,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well.\NI must be off to the royal household.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.25,0:05:11.91,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell the store owner not to worry...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.12,0:05:14.88,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,the police are certain to\Nbring the jewel back shortly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.29,0:05:20.28,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, now...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.20,0:05:24.66,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Holmes?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.76,0:05:25.89,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.30,0:05:27.53,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Here they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.87,0:05:30.16,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,These are footprints.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.44,0:05:33.13,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,They must belong to the person who\Nescaped through the broken window.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.21,0:05:33.69,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.17,0:05:35.20,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no doubt.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.41,0:05:38.93,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,There was somebody other than Moriarty\Nand his henchmen in that room last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.11,0:05:41.24,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone who has very small feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.99,0:05:52.05,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,We're supposed to be eating\Na piece of steak this thick.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.23,0:05:56.25,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Professor, your food's ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.73,0:05:57.49,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.70,0:05:58.66,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,This is no time for eating!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.47,0:06:04.06,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Curse you, whoever you may be,\Nfor stealing my prize!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.30,0:06:06.33,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Professor...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.41,0:06:08.17,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Moreover, a false accusation\Nhas been laid upon me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.04,0:06:10.87,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Professor,\Nare you not going to eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.24,0:06:13.47,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,If not, I'll finish it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.11,0:06:17.64,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot! Who said I'm not eating?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.52,0:06:24.75,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you've become famous\Nin any case, Professor. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.12,0:06:27.79,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,O... Oh, yes, right, Professor.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.23,0:06:30.20,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Left behind a red rose and an\Nannouncement of the next crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.30,0:06:32.79,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,How neat!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.50,0:06:35.56,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiots!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.87,0:06:38.17,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you no shred of pride?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.87,0:06:41.97,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Never think that Professor Moriarty\Ncan be beaten like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.31,0:06:44.90,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, I shall be the one\Nto steal his prize!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.08,0:06:46.87,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,You two!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.81,0:06:50.54,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Go find out what was\Nin that announcement!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.25,0:06:52.91,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.22,0:06:53.95,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.22,0:06:56.98,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!\NFigure it out yourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.06,0:06:58.02,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.66,0:07:03.36,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Holmes! Holmes, where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.93,0:07:04.92,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I know you're in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.26,0:07:07.06,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.97,0:07:08.93,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out, Inspector!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.65,0:07:25.71,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,You opened the door too roughly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.02,0:07:27.85,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Darn it all!\NWhat is this about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.05,0:07:30.49,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm conducting an investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.29,0:07:36.16,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Investigation?\NYou'll only find old records in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.30,0:07:40.16,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I remember hearing about a famous thief\Nwho would leave at the scene of a crime...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.23,0:07:42.72,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,a red rose and an announcement for\Nhis next crime as his trademark.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.74,0:07:45.86,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're talking about\N"Christopher the Mysterious Thief".
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.67,0:07:48.23,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you of know him, Inspector?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.31,0:07:49.30,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.41,0:07:52.43,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Around the time I\Nfirst joined Scotland Yard...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.61,0:07:56.38,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,this mysterious thief managed to\Nfluster the entire city of London.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.66,0:08:09.18,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Bold and gorgeous...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.26,0:08:11.09,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,though he was an enemy,\Nhe was very charismatic indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.93,0:08:16.26,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,This is it, Holmes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.37,0:08:22.31,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Inspector, do you mind\Nif I take this with me tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.41,0:08:23.87,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I don't, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.48,0:08:29.07,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you think this current\Ncase is related to Christopher.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.18,0:08:32.58,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,He was a thief more\Nthan twenty years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.05,0:08:38.01,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Those three are trying to imitate\NChristopher the Mysterious Thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.19,0:08:41.68,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know if you should conclude\Nanything without a full investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.79,0:08:43.66,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Are you trying to insult me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.96,0:08:45.49,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Inspector...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.56,0:08:48.23,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,you went to inform the royal guards\Nabout the crime letter, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.30,0:08:49.39,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,How did they react?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.80,0:08:51.39,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Unspeakably!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.77,0:08:53.80,Behind the Scenes,,0000,0000,0000,,Inspector,\Ndo you really believe that we...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.87,0:08:57.36,Behind the Scenes,,0000,0000,0000,,the royal guards,\Nwill dance to the magpies' piping?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.61,0:09:01.24,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,They said they have no intention\Nof altering Shoscom Prince's escort...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.31,0:09:03.21,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,scheduled for the day after tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.72,0:09:04.98,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,They said "no"...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.55,0:09:07.18,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, I'll borrow this for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.35,0:09:08.05,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.39,0:09:09.05,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.55,0:09:11.28,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Remember,\Nreturn the book by tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.32,0:09:12.12,Behind the Scenes,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.76,0:09:14.89,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What could he be thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.77,0:09:21.99,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning, Watson.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.17,0:09:25.40,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you up so early for, Holmes?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.40,0:09:28.03,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, daybreak came\Nwhile I was reading this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.14,0:09:29.40,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,You stayed up all night?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.78,0:09:31.21,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you find anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.28,0:09:32.71,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,A lot of interesting facts.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.94,0:09:37.11,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,He surely was a thief among thieves.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.92,0:09:41.91,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Always leaving a red rose and a\Nletter at the scene of the crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.22,0:09:45.25,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,He drove the police mad back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.56,0:09:49.96,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,However, he disappeared\Nafter one case twenty years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.23,0:09:52.66,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What was the case?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.27,0:09:55.40,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,The fine royal horse abduction affair.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.70,0:09:56.33,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.90,0:09:59.50,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,This was his only\Nfailed attempt at thievery.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.64,0:10:01.44,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, he did steal the horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.51,0:10:02.03,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.11,0:10:04.08,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,because the bridle snapped\Nduring his escape...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.14,0:10:05.67,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,he fell into the Thames.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.84,0:10:07.87,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,He's been missing ever since then.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.08,0:10:10.67,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Holmes, it was Christopher\Nwho stole the jewel then!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.82,0:10:12.04,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I doubt it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.32,0:10:14.11,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing has explained\Nhis twenty-year absence...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.19,0:10:16.95,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,and most importantly,\Nhe was said to have a large build.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.09,0:10:20.18,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think the footprints\Nwe found are too small for a big man?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.96,0:10:24.09,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you leaving?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.23,0:10:25.96,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to return the book\Nto Scotland Yard.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.16,0:10:27.83,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,We promised to return it\Nafter one night, didn't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.40,0:10:30.27,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, are you going out?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.44,0:10:32.27,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I'll be back by dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.44,0:10:33.34,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.34,0:10:33.90,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.78,0:10:41.71,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother, what are we doing now?\NI'm tired of standing here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.85,0:10:46.41,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I know. How are we supposed to find\Nout what's in his crime message?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.72,0:10:48.98,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,The press don't even know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.96,0:10:51.72,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's ask that policeman over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.82,0:10:53.88,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.63,0:11:02.90,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,You dropped this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.84,0:11:05.53,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, yes, thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.67,0:11:08.40,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,The case about that jewel thief,\Nwho left a red rose and letter...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.47,0:11:09.46,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,stating his next crime...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.38,0:11:14.11,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody's been talking about\Nit since yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.18,0:11:15.48,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.68,0:11:19.35,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,It's said in the letter\Nthat the next target is tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.35,0:11:22.22,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,The fine royal horse,\NShoscom Prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.82,0:11:23.98,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.16,0:11:29.06,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, or so I've heard, but I'm\Nnot sure if it will really happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.63,0:11:32.26,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Scary, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.63,0:11:37.03,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Those two men... they're...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.07,0:11:39.87,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Miss!\NThanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.91,0:11:47.57,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, Miss.\NDo you know those two men?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.91,0:11:53.21,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,No, they just asked me for directions.\NMay I ask who you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.49,0:11:56.65,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon me.\NI am a detective, Holmes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.82,0:11:59.05,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just that they looked like\Nsome people that I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.62,0:12:04.96,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,So, are you the famous Mr. Holmes?\NIt is an honour to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.16,0:12:08.39,Behind the Scenes,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss... Miss...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.44,0:12:13.17,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, Mr. Holmes.\NI must go now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.11,0:12:19.37,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope to see you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.89,0:12:29.62,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Just asked directions, did they?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.63,0:12:45.66,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand it is your duty\Nto pursue the thieves...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.80,0:12:48.77,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,but make sure you\Ndo not get in our way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.21,0:12:50.11,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.18,0:12:51.20,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.45,0:13:04.09,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Both of you!\NYou can follow us if you want to...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.09,0:13:06.35,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,but make sure\Nyou don't interfere!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.49,0:13:07.52,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.43,0:13:10.55,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my... Yes, I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.66,0:13:14.53,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Who does he think he is?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.34,0:13:18.70,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,We're leaving!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.98,0:13:25.87,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.82,0:13:32.87,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.18,0:14:07.55,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Under such tight security,\Nthe criminal will hardly have...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.55,0:14:08.99,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,the chance to appear, will he?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.05,0:14:12.96,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, my instincts tell me that it's\Njust about time for their appearance...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.79,0:14:14.92,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.30,0:14:19.32,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.13,0:14:21.83,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,There you are, Moriarty!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.74,0:14:31.71,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Smoke?! What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.31,0:14:36.97,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,OK, ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.52,0:14:39.81,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.09,0:14:47.39,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Be calm! Protect the royal horse!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.86,0:14:48.45,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.53,0:14:50.22,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to Moriarty\Nand his gang?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.30,0:14:51.16,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.40,0:14:53.06,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.70,0:14:58.03,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep your eyes on the royal horse!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.10,0:14:59.37,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,It's difficult with all this smoke!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.74,0:15:02.10,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,How's the horse?!\NIs Shoscom Prince safe?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.21,0:15:04.27,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain, I'll go get reinforcements!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.34,0:15:05.31,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Good, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.95,0:15:11.14,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Watson, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.22,0:15:12.08,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.15,0:15:16.14,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What the devil is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.45,0:15:18.85,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Professor, I don't know,\Nbut this is not good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.92,0:15:19.82,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's just go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.89,0:15:21.92,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,You fool! There will never be\Na better chance than this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.00,0:15:26.83,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Ready? Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.74,0:15:34.00,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it! Pull up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.54,0:15:39.27,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, stop that!\NWhat are you doing?! Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.34,0:15:41.54,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Oops, wrong one!\NShake him off!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.85,0:15:45.61,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Professor, it's not possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.85,0:15:47.34,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,It's broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.52,0:15:48.78,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,You, idiot! Fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.85,0:15:50.82,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Drat! I built it too hastily.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.92,0:15:52.08,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'll go then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.36,0:15:56.33,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,You there, down you go! Down!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.43,0:15:58.33,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! You worthless idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.63,0:16:00.29,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Get your foot off of my face!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.74,0:16:04.63,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Darn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.31,0:16:16.51,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,How lucky! The royal horse!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.61,0:16:17.74,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.02,0:16:23.25,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,So long, Inspector Lestrade!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.92,0:16:26.29,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,You villain, Moriarty!\NGet him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.29,0:16:26.78,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.23,0:16:34.06,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Catch me if you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.33,0:16:36.89,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop right there, Moriarty!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.60,0:16:38.69,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.14,0:16:42.27,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Mr. Royal Horse,\Ncan't you run any faster?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.61,0:16:43.77,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.84,0:16:44.87,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,We've almost got him.\NGo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.48,0:16:47.57,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on!\NFaster, I said faster!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.48,0:16:50.54,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.15,0:16:53.41,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,"I have stolen the royal horse."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.49,0:16:54.42,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.56,0:17:04.46,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Holmes, what's wrong\Nwith that horse?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.60,0:17:06.46,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Look carefully at how\Nhe runs and his speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.53,0:17:08.23,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll see that it's\Nno ordinary horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.37,0:17:10.10,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Then, that one is the...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.17,0:17:11.33,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.52,0:17:31.55,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.79,0:17:32.65,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.59,0:17:34.25,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.10,0:17:41.66,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang in there! Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.17,0:17:48.90,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, good horse.\NThere you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.48,0:17:57.64,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Ready to talk, Alline Christopher?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.18,0:18:01.28,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Holmes, Christopher?\NSo then...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.86,0:18:12.30,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,You win, Detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.43,0:18:13.92,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.33,0:18:18.13,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Alline, is the daughter of Christopher,\Nthe mysterious thief, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.20,0:18:19.33,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I certainly am.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.58,0:18:26.41,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Please! I'm begging you, run faster!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.91,0:18:30.35,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you given up yet?\NWe're almost there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.22,0:18:35.58,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother! I found him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.75,0:18:38.05,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,OK, let's drop this noisy fool off.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.63,0:18:43.12,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.33,0:18:47.09,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to kill me!\NI'll die!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.81,0:18:55.27,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice! Let's get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.58,0:19:02.21,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,My father was a top merchant\Nand a fine gentleman.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.15,0:19:05.88,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,But he passed away\Nafter a terrible illness.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.25,0:19:09.22,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,My mother and I have been\Ngrieving deeply ever since.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.05,0:19:15.79,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,One day, when I was cleaning his study,\NI came upon his old diary.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.49,0:19:22.33,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,In it, I saw his other face, known to all\Nas Christopher the Mysterious Thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.90,0:19:25.50,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,You knew everything at that point.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.80,0:19:32.67,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I see, it must have been quite shocking\Nto learn that your father was a thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.11,0:19:37.02,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it was exciting to discover that my\Nfather had such an exciting past!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.02,0:19:37.61,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.48,0:19:41.61,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,How bitter it must have been for him,\Nhurting his leg...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.69,0:19:43.81,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,and having to retire\Nfrom the business!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.36,0:19:49.35,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,So, I was determined to complete the\Nwork he'd been forced to leave undone!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.76,0:19:51.25,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.63,0:19:55.90,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. Almost! A little lower!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.97,0:19:57.13,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.10,0:19:59.76,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Moriarty, you won't get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.74,0:20:04.71,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, he's finally giving up the horse!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.78,0:20:06.18,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoscom Prince is back!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.98,0:20:12.18,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Shosom Prince,\NI'm so glad you're safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.32,0:20:14.98,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute... this horse?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.05,0:20:15.99,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a phony!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.05,0:20:16.82,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.16,0:20:21.39,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you straighten yourself out?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.49,0:20:25.29,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear you Professor, but nothing\Nseems to be working correctly.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.36,0:20:26.92,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,You fool, that's because\Nyour pitiful skills are...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.00,0:20:28.02,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.27,0:20:31.50,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Moriarty, what did you do with\Nthe royal horse?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.57,0:20:34.27,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,You dirty thieves, return the horse!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.34,0:20:37.07,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm innocent! It was already\Nthe wrong horse when I fell on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.28,0:20:39.07,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,You lying rat!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.48,0:20:45.42,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,No, stop! What're you doing?! Let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.92,0:20:49.32,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Never! Return the horse!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.39,0:20:51.01,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you I'm innocent!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.26,0:20:52.56,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I know you're lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.56,0:20:53.18,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.49,0:20:55.05,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, let go! Don't bother me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.76,0:20:58.06,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Too heavy.\NMy arms are falling off...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.16,0:20:59.43,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,No, don't be silly!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.43,0:21:01.19,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,That's more weight than\Nthis machine can hold!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.83,0:21:02.53,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.00,0:21:03.83,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.20,0:21:05.86,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother, look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.64,0:21:08.61,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you so!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.21,0:21:13.77,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,We made it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.72,0:21:25.15,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,You certainly look awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.26,0:21:27.45,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Have a look at yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.13,0:21:32.49,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,So, are you going to arrest me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.66,0:21:37.03,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's see.\NWe're not policemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.14,0:21:39.50,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,So, as long as you return\Nthe jewel and horse...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.77,0:21:42.97,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I never meant to keep them anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.28,0:21:47.90,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, will you promise that\Nyou will never do this again?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.01,0:21:50.71,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose I have no choice,\Nit was a lot of fun, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.92,0:21:52.82,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,A good thief must also\Nknow when to quit!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.69,0:22:05.06,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,The case's closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.70,0:22:10.00,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,A good thief must know when to quit...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.80,0:22:13.10,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish they could hear this.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.57,0:22:16.10,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed, if they could.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.28,0:22:19.48,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Professor.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.48,0:22:22.61,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's give up and retire\Nfrom this business.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.68,0:22:26.88,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,You fool! I won't quit until\NI'm known as the "Napoleon of Crime!"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.29,0:22:29.31,Behind the Scenes,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, we'll never get out from this.
