Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.07,0:24:00.48,Behind the Scenes,,0000,0000,0000,,Just before the start of the World\NAircraft Championship Race in Holland...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.68,0:24:03.48,Behind the Scenes,,0000,0000,0000,,a high-performance engine\Nis stolen from Mac Bain...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.48,0:24:05.42,Behind the Scenes,,0000,0000,0000,,a brilliant aeronautical engineer.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.22,0:24:08.65,Behind the Scenes,,0000,0000,0000,,The cunning Professor Moriarty\Naims to win the air race...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.72,0:24:11.52,Behind the Scenes,,0000,0000,0000,,by using the stolen engine.\NWhich is thoroughly unacceptable!
